*PPD-Adobe: "4.3"
*%PPD file for QuadToneRIP
*%Inks K,C,M,Y,LC,LM,LK,LLK,V,MK
*FormatVersion: "4.3"
*FileVersion:   "2.8.2"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*PCFileName:    "QuadP9500.ppd"
*Manufacturer:  "QuadToneRIP"
*Product:       "(EPSON SureColor P9500)"
*ModelName:     "escp2-P700"
